description:
A .NET Library for HashiCorp's Vault - A Secret Management System.

VaultSharp supports all the APIs (including all secret and auth backends) supported by Hashicorp's Vault.

All Authentication backends supported by Vault are supported. These include App-Id, AppRole, AWS EC2, GitHub, LDAP, MFA, TLS Certificates, Tokens, Username & Password.

All Secret backends supported by Vault are supported. These include  AWS, Cassandra, Consul, Cubbyhole, Generic, MongoDB, MSSQL, MySql, PKI, PostgreSQL, RabbitMQ, SSH, Transit etc.

All Audit backends supported by Vault are supported. These include File and Syslog.

Changelog is here: https://github.com/rajanadar/VaultSharp/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#061-october-03-2016
summary: A .NET Library for HashiCorp's Vault - A Secret Management System.

MetadataExtractor is a straightforward and lightweight library for reading metadata from image and video files.
      It reads Exif, IPTC, XMP, ICC, Photoshop, WebP, PNG, BMP, GIF, ICO, PCX metadata from JPEG, TIFF WebP, PSD, PNG, BMP, GIF, ICO, PCX and camera RAW files.
      Camera manufacturer specific support exists for Agfa, Canon, Casio, Epson, Fujifilm, Kodak, Kyocera, Leica, Minolta, Nikon, Olympus, Panasonic, Pentax, Reconyx, Sanyo, Sigma/Foveon and Sony models.
      In addition, MOV and related QuickTime video formats are supported such as MP4, M4V, 3G2, 3GP.

      This package supports:

      - .NET Framework 3.5
      - .NET Framework 4.5
      - Silverlight 5.0
      - Windows 8.0
      - Windows Phone 8.1
      - Windows Phone Silverlight 8.0
